      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know you're \"supposed\" to tell me to get help or whatever, but it feels like a lie. even talking to someone just makes the noise louder. it feels like a cycle that never ends. if i stay, it just keeps happening. i just keep thinking about how much easier it would be if i could just... exit. like, if i wasn't here, the bullying wouldn't matter anymore and nobody would have to deal with me. it seems like the only real way to actually find some peace is to just stop existing.",
